{"_path":"/maps/_biology/attention","_dir":"_biology","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"注意力","description":"","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"daily-bugs"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Daily Bugs"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"_2026-01-10"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"2026-01-10"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"上周还是什么时候，我快速浏览了某篇文档，里面有A，但是我脑海里想的是B，就以为文档记录的是B。我特喵特意过了两遍文档，信誓旦旦和别人说B，结果是错的，后来才发现。这特喵是哪门子注意力啊！"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"reports"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Reports"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"注意力使用不完全报告"},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://sspai.com/post/70482","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意力使用不完全报告"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"在精神最佳、状态最好的时候完成最重要的任务。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"任务目标越清楚，大脑越容易进入专注状态。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用注意力会消耗体能，吃饱饭、睡好觉、多锻炼，都可以有效提升注意力的上限。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意力不是恒定不变，而是在时刻波动的。短暂的跑神可以让大脑得到休息，要主动提醒自己回到焦点，保持专注。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意力就像摄影，找到目标之后要通过"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"建立心理路径"}]},{"type":"text","value":"将焦点锁定，避免大脑受到其它元素干扰而脱离主线。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"注意力和身体素质一样，越锻炼越强壮，越使用越熟练。"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"横幅盲视如何削弱警示信息的有效性"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"横幅盲视如何削弱警示信息的有效性？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"屏幕角落常驻显示的警示标语（如赌博成瘾预防信息）实际视线占有率极低。\n这种现象被称为"},{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"横幅盲视（Banner Blindness）"}]},{"type":"text","value":"——用户因长期暴露在固定位置而自动忽略这些元素。\n该概念最早由 Benway 于 1998 年提出，后经 Nielsen 用眼动追踪实验确认：\n用户几乎从不查看任何看起来像广告的内容，无论其是否为真正的广告。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"非注意盲视加剧忽视"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：当用户高度专注于主任务时，\n大脑因**高知觉负载（Perceptual Load）**而缩小注意范围，\n导致周边视野信息处理能力显著下降（Lavie, 2005）。\n这与隧道视野（Tunnel Vision）效应类似——注意力集中于中心任务时，\n周边信息被主动过滤。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"strong","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"改进方向"}]},{"type":"text","value":"：从\"单向告知\"转向\"对话型警告\""}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"引入交互元素（如强制确认弹窗而非静态文字）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"基于情境的动态曝光（如游戏时长触发）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"与全面预防体系联动（如结合账户限额、强制冷却期）"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://piracysim.com/%ed%99%94%eb%a9%b4-%ea%b5%ac%ec%84%9d-%ec%83%81%ec%8b%9c-%eb%85%b8%ec%b6%9c-%eb%8f%84%eb%b0%95-%ec%a4%91%eb%8f%85-%ec%98%88%eb%b0%a9-%eb%ac%b8%ea%b5%ac-%ec%8b%a4%ec%a7%88%ec%a0%81-%ec%8b%9c%ec%84%a0/","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"화면 구석 상시 노출되는 도박 중독 예방 문구의 실질적 시선 점유율"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://baike.baidu.com/item/banner%2520blindness/10544170","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Banner Blindness - Benway (1998)"}]},{"type":"text","value":"、\n"},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://link.springer.com/article/10.3758/s13423-015-0982-5","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"知觉负载理论 - Lavie (2005)"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"daily-bugs","depth":2,"text":"Daily Bugs"},{"id":"reports","depth":2,"text":"Reports"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_biology:attention.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_biology/attention.md","_stem":"6.maps/_biology/attention","_extension":"md"}